Say "=== COMPARISON: Prose vs Python Features ===".

Let name be "Prose".
Let number be 42.
Let pi be 3.14159.
Say "Variable assignment works: " plus name plus ", " plus number plus ", " plus pi plus ".".

If number > 40 then do the following.
    Say "Conditional (if) statement works!".
End if.

Say "Testing loops:".
Let counter be 0.
Repeat 3 times do the following.
    Let counter be counter plus 1.
    Say "  Loop iteration " plus counter plus ".".
End repeat.

Define a function called double that takes x and does the following.
    Let doubled be x times 2.
    Give back doubled.
End function.

Call double with 5.
Say "Function call result: 5 doubled is " plus result plus ".".

Say "=== Prose language test complete ===".